    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "排查入口说明",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 1
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 三个最常用入口\n\n- **按用户查**：填顶部 `用户 ID`，看这个用户的请求日志和 trace。\n- **按 Request ID 查**：填 `Request ID`，直接定位一次请求的日志和链路。\n- **按接口查耗时**：填 `接口路径正则`，看接口 P95/P99、请求量和慢请求日志。\n\n提示：`user_id` / `request_id` 是高基数字段，只在日志 JSON 或 Tempo span attributes 里查，不提升为 Loki label。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 200,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "按用户 ID / Request ID 查请求",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 5
      },
      "collapsed": false
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "用户请求日志",
      "description": "填 user_id 后，按 RuntimeLogEntry.userId 精确/正则查询 user_action 日志。",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 6
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "{app=\"$service\", log_type=\"user_action\"} | json | userId=~\"$user_id\"",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "legendFormat": ""
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "showTime": true,
        "showLabels": true,
        "showCommonLabels": false,
        "wrapLogMessage": true,
        "prettifyLogMessage": true,
        "enableLogDetails": true,
        "enableHighlighting": true,
        "fontSize": "default",
        "sortOrder": "Descending"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "Request ID 请求日志",
      "description": "填 request_id 后，查询同一次请求的所有结构化日志。",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 12,
        "x": 12,
